<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>New Reservation Paid</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #47B2E4 0%, #293751 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #47B2E4 0%, #293751 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .summary-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #293751;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .summary-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .detail-card {
      background: #f4f8fc;
      border: 1px solid #d3e9f8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .detail-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: #293751;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .detail-card span {
      color: #47B2E4;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f0f4f9;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #d0e2f2;
    }

    .footer p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 15px;
      }

      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .details-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Reservation Paid</h1>
      <p>A new reservation has been successfully paid</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="summary-section">
        <h2>Payment & Client Details</h2>
        <p>Below are the details for the newly paid reservation:</p>
      </div>

      <div class="details-grid">
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Receipt Number</strong><span>{{receiptNumber}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Client Name</strong><span>{{fullName}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Client Email</strong><span>{{email}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Client Phone</strong><span>{{phone}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Pickup</strong><span>{{pickup}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Dropoff</strong><span>{{dropoff}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Scheduled Time</strong><span>{{scheduledDateTime}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Passengers</strong><span>{{numberOfPassengers}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Distance</strong><span>{{distance}} km</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Duration</strong><span>{{duration}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Total Paid</strong><span>{{price}}</span></div>
        <div class="detail-card"><strong>Driver Assigned</strong><span>{{driverAssigned}}</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automatic system alert for paid reservations.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br><strong>AbyRide System</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
